{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2021/01/11/JMJ/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a3cde1b4-c870-5d28-a077-6d4461bb4c5c","html":"<p><del>谁说这系列没下文了</del></p>\n<p>著名凉拌菜的本地化改造。中超需求为酱油（生抽/老抽），香辣红油，香醋，料酒，青花椒</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p>  一个显然但仍应当指出的事实是：这个系列的同种菜谱在互联网上俯仰皆是，写这些菜谱的初衷也不完全是单纯的教人做菜——不过笔者认为这些作为一人做饭一人食的倒霉蛋的个人经验，依旧对类似状态的读者有些分享的价值。更何况，它也能做为笔者这段时光的回忆之一。 <del>更何况我还给标题塞进了一个梗，不能不用</del></p>\n<p>另一个不那么显然的事实：作为一个浙江人，笔者并不清楚椒麻鸡和口水鸡的具体区别。在此人眼中，它们都指代“浸有麻辣料汁的凉拌鸡肉”，但这并不妨碍他十分喜欢这道菜（为此，从来不吃醋的笔者特地为这道菜买了醋并已经用掉了小半瓶）</p>\n<p>这道菜具有适用于独居人的一大优势：麻烦的料汁可以一次准备多顿的量，有效缓解了每天重复劳动的痛苦感，同时操作流程难度很低，是笔者相当推荐的选择。除非是忌辣人群，我鼓励有兴趣的朋友自己尝试一下。</p>\n<p><strong>原料</strong>：</p>\n<p>鸡股 若干只（300~400g)</p>\n<p>青花椒 一把（20g左右)</p>\n<p>大蒜 4-5瓣（20g)</p>\n<p>生姜 2块（30-40g）</p>\n<p>类小米辣 m个（20g)</p>\n<p><strong>调料</strong>：</p>\n<p>盐 糖 生抽 老抽 胡椒粉 香辣红油 食用油 料酒</p>\n<p><strong>关于选料</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>鸡股是指鸡腿的上方部分，也就是俗称手枪腿的上半截，肉质和鸡腿类似，但胜在容易切块。椒麻鸡的理想材料毫无疑问也是鸡腿，但使用鸡腿需要斩骨，这一工作还是有一定危险性的，选用鸡股可以避免这一点。<del>如果你觉得上面这段描述很熟悉，那是因为这段是从黄焖鸡那篇原样复制过来的</del>。但值得一提的是，英国Tesco包装好的chicken thigh已经不再是四个了，而是数量不定的七到久个，但是总重量并没有改变（英国的鸡不行了，越长越小）（或者说是因为杜伦的供货农场比伦敦的水平低？）</li>\n<li>辣椒的量请自行控制。有中超买的小米辣当然最好，但tesco售卖的尖椒起到的效果也大同小异。</li>\n<li>建议生姜去皮防止对口感的影响。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>流程</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>鸡股洗净后入锅，加入适量料酒，生姜若干片，半把青花椒。加冷水至没过鸡肉，加盖大火烧开。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/b8e44/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 119%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/066f9/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/b9e9c/1.jpg 100w,\n/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/e07e9/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/066f9/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/b4294/1.jpg 600w,\n/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/4b190/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/62d0953c6c297662d4f6ac4d01016ce3/b8e44/1.jpg 2957w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>煮沸后关火，留盖放置40分钟，用余温把鸡肉烫熟。此步是保证鸡肉口感的关键，请不要煮沸过久。</li>\n<li>\n<p>剩余生姜，小米辣，大蒜切末，同青花椒一道放入碗中，加入胡椒粉、盐、糖。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/6dd23/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/066f9/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/b9e9c/2.jpg 100w,\n/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/e07e9/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/066f9/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/b4294/2.jpg 600w,\n/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/4b190/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/6ca8b97d434891b306905e9b0525ddaf/6dd23/2.jpg 2973w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/f5b8c/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 106%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/066f9/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/b9e9c/3.jpg 100w,\n/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/e07e9/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/066f9/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/b4294/3.jpg 600w,\n/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/4b190/3.jpg 800w,\n/static/93e435704bce274fd70a62168c83b594/f5b8c/3.jpg 3004w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>加入生抽、香醋、少量老抽着色。最后加入稍微多量的香辣红油，搅拌均匀。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/891ee/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 111.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/066f9/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/b9e9c/4.jpg 100w,\n/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/e07e9/4.jpg 200w,\n/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/066f9/4.jpg 400w,\n/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/b4294/4.jpg 600w,\n/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/4b190/4.jpg 800w,\n/static/164afd5fdbf4055eec56662c9c9fd00d/891ee/4.jpg 2858w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>原则上上一步是泼油激发出料头的香气，但这么做太麻烦了，和独居人的画风不符。作为代替，将料汁放入微波炉加热大约60秒。加热完毕后再次搅拌均匀，放入冰箱冷藏室两小时。<strong>注意加盖</strong>，否则你的冰箱马上就全是这个味道了。</li>\n<li>\n<p>烫熟的鸡股捞出后在冷水中浸泡变凉，随后按平行骨的方向切成宽半厘米左右的鸡块，在容器中码好。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/5d144/5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/066f9/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/b9e9c/5.jpg 100w,\n/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/e07e9/5.jpg 200w,\n/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/066f9/5.jpg 400w,\n/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/b4294/5.jpg 600w,\n/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/4b190/5.jpg 800w,\n/static/9293394949f99b7e5444f5ae803a924a/5d144/5.jpg 2954w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将冷却完毕的料汁淋上即可。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/da30b/6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 140%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/066f9/6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/b9e9c/6.jpg 100w,\n/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/e07e9/6.jpg 200w,\n/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/066f9/6.jpg 400w,\n/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/b4294/6.jpg 600w,\n/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/4b190/6.jpg 800w,\n/static/a4b8b4e3d507270e74b6f8d1e0dce90b/da30b/6.jpg 2249w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>注意事项</strong>：这是一道凉菜，成菜温度过高会严重影响品质。无论是鸡肉还是料汁都要事先降温处理。餐后剩余的料汁可以放冰箱用于第二顿，但鸡肉最好每次只准备一次的量，新鲜的鸡肉口感是这道菜的关键之一。<del>另，从营养均衡的角度考虑，建议读者用餐时另行准备素菜搭配</del></p>\n<p>更多照骗：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/307d7/7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/066f9/7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/b9e9c/7.jpg 100w,\n/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/e07e9/7.jpg 200w,\n/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/066f9/7.jpg 400w,\n/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/b4294/7.jpg 600w,\n/static/ebe94ac343fbf9e54549ee3bbd6fc0ab/307d7/7.jpg 760w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/daa83/8.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/066f9/8.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/b9e9c/8.jpg 100w,\n/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/e07e9/8.jpg 200w,\n/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/066f9/8.jpg 400w,\n/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/b4294/8.jpg 600w,\n/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/4b190/8.jpg 800w,\n/static/5c92255f508920f10264f6f73d2a2022/daa83/8.jpg 3897w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"ZH家的饭 3 椒麻鸡","date":"2021-01-11","categories":"杂学","message":null,"tags":["菜谱"]},"fields":{"encrypted":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/11/21/live2d/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Live2D制作指东"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"a3cde1b4-c870-5d28-a077-6d4461bb4c5c","previousPostId":"33c1c87f-5adb-5b24-acf3-4239b3f2b528","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["1605745662","2212765230","2826202570","3000541721","3274528899","3390260504","3406122720","3823010829","689422991"]}